1
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:53,960
What's wrong, Xiaobei?

2
00:00:55,359 --> 00:00:56,079
I'm fine.

3
00:00:58,479 --> 00:01:00,079
I'm heading out for a bit.

4
00:01:00,359 --> 00:01:01,240
Where are you going?

5
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:03,240
I'll be right back.

6
00:01:04,959 --> 00:01:06,280
Eat first, then go.

7
00:01:10,079 --> 00:01:10,879
Zhang Xiaobei.

8
00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:13,920
What are you doing here?

9
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:14,959
Come with me somewhere.

10
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:15,840
Let's go.

11
00:01:17,319 --> 00:01:18,319
In the middle of the night?

12
00:01:18,319 --> 00:01:19,280
Why'd you bring me to your place?

13
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:20,640
I've got something to give you.

14
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:21,599
What is it?

15
00:01:22,719 --> 00:01:23,400
Just five minutes.

16
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,719
You'll love it. Come on!

17
00:01:28,439 --> 00:01:30,519
Zhang Xiaobei, why are you here?

18
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,359
Looks like once it's past midnight,

19
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:34,959
you switch back right away.

20
00:01:39,159 --> 00:01:39,959
I...

21
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:43,400
brought Sheng Yuanzhou home.

22
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:54,200
Now that he's back,

23
00:01:54,719 --> 00:01:55,640
I'll get going.

24
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:58,519
What?

25
00:02:14,919 --> 00:02:15,599
Father.

26
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:17,439
Don't call me Father.

27
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:24,599
I don't need a useless son.

28
00:03:05,319 --> 00:03:06,439
Xiaobei!

29
00:03:06,759 --> 00:03:08,919
The sun is already high in the sky!

30
00:03:08,919 --> 00:03:09,840
You're still sleeping?

31
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,240
Hurry down for breakfast.

32
00:03:12,639 --> 00:03:13,400
Coming.

33
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:15,840
Coming, coming!

34
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:18,719
Xiaobei's up!

35
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:20,280
Come down, come down!

36
00:03:20,599 --> 00:03:22,520
Your mom made you scallion pancakes.

37
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:23,400
They smell amazing.

38
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:24,319
Come on, come on!

39
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,759
What's with him?

40
00:03:29,639 --> 00:03:30,520
Here, try some.

41
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:31,639
Dad, Mom.

42
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:33,319
I'm finally back.

43
00:03:33,639 --> 00:03:34,120
Eat.

44
00:03:38,759 --> 00:03:40,080
Why is it so greasy?

45
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:43,240
I used less oil on purpose today.

46
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,240
Mom.

47
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,400
How about we eat out tonight?

48
00:03:48,599 --> 00:03:49,319
No.

49
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:52,439
Why waste that money?

50
00:03:53,599 --> 00:03:55,039
I already bought groceries for dinner.

51
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:56,680
It won't cost much.

52
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,439
Mom.

53
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,400
I can earn my own money.

54
00:04:01,599 --> 00:04:03,120
I'll give you a good life.

55
00:04:04,159 --> 00:04:04,919
Hang on.

56
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,599
This kid...

57
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:22,920
Son...

58
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,480
Where'd you get all this money?

59
00:04:26,879 --> 00:04:28,920
Xiaobei, we're poor, but

60
00:04:29,319 --> 00:04:31,120
you must never do anything illegal.

61
00:04:31,319 --> 00:04:34,360
Mom, I earned this fair and square.

62
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:35,839
Let's go have a big feast tonight.

63
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:36,560
Something nice.

64
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,560
Son...

65
00:04:38,639 --> 00:04:41,160
You've worked so hard all these years.

66
00:04:41,319 --> 00:04:42,759
I know you're a good son.

67
00:04:43,319 --> 00:04:44,519
But save the money.

68
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,800
Keep it for Siqi.

69
00:04:46,519 --> 00:04:48,319
Siqi is a good girl.

70
00:04:48,319 --> 00:04:50,560
I'm used to this hard life.

71
00:04:50,879 --> 00:04:51,759
Go wait inside.

72
00:04:51,839 --> 00:04:53,160
I've still got two dishes to make.

73
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:53,959
Go on.

74
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:11,399
I heard you mortgaged the land

75
00:05:11,399 --> 00:05:12,279
your mother left you.

76
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:13,680
I...

77
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:27,959
Why did you mortgage it?

78
00:05:28,639 --> 00:05:29,480
I...

79
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,560
I don't know.

80
00:05:36,959 --> 00:05:38,000
You don't know?

81
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,439
I'll get it back immediately.

82
00:06:03,279 --> 00:06:05,160
Didn't your panic disorder get better?

83
00:06:07,079 --> 00:06:08,759
Make time to see Dr. Chen.

84
00:06:09,519 --> 00:06:12,040
Yes, Father.

85
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:15,800
You useless thing.

86
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:33,399
What's wrong with me?

87
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:35,000
I mortgaged Mom's land

88
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,560
to buy Zhang Xiaobei's family a house.

89
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:38,399
None of this sounds like something I'd do.

90
00:06:38,839 --> 00:06:39,600
And...

91
00:06:39,839 --> 00:06:41,240
why did I buy these socks?

92
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,439
Who was I buying them for?

93
00:06:42,519 --> 00:06:43,319
Mr. Sheng.

94
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,519
Why don't you talk to Dr. Chen?

95
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:48,800
No. If I tell Dr. Chen,

96
00:06:49,319 --> 00:06:50,720
she'll think I'm like my mom,

97
00:06:50,879 --> 00:06:51,720
completely crazy.

98
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,040
Jiang Lai.

99
00:07:01,439 --> 00:07:02,519
Sheng Yuanzhou.

100
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,639
What are you doing here?

101
00:07:08,079 --> 00:07:10,480
Didn't expect you to actually switch back.

102
00:07:10,839 --> 00:07:11,680
What did you say?

103
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:14,120
I said, "Long time no see."

104
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:15,360
Get to the point.

105
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,360
Otherwise, leave.

106
00:07:16,399 --> 00:07:18,399
You can't just walk into the Sheng family.

107
00:07:18,399 --> 00:07:19,240
Is that so?

108
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:22,360
As the Sheng family's future daughter-in-law,

109
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,639
I can't come see

110
00:07:23,759 --> 00:07:25,319
my husband-to-be?

111
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:25,879
What?

112
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:30,519
I hereby officially announce

113
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,839
my engagement to Miss Jiang Lai.

114
00:07:37,439 --> 00:07:38,839
How could I be engaged to her?

115
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,319
Honey.

116
00:07:40,959 --> 00:07:41,920
Remember now?

117
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:44,560
Jiang Lai, listen to me.

118
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,879
I don't know what you did

119
00:07:45,879 --> 00:07:47,279
to make me agree to this engagement,

120
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:49,120
but I'll never marry you.

121
00:07:49,839 --> 00:07:51,319
Last time, you took advantage of me being drunk,

122
00:07:51,319 --> 00:07:52,319
pretended you slept with me,

123
00:07:52,319 --> 00:07:54,279
and blackmailed me with photos. Forgot?

124
00:07:55,079 --> 00:07:57,040
Do you think I'm that easy to manipulate?

125
00:07:57,160 --> 00:08:00,079
You were cuter back in Commoners' Alley.

126
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:00,800
I'm leaving.

127
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,720
One more thing.

128
00:08:06,839 --> 00:08:08,160
I wasn't planning to marry you either.

129
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,399
What is she even talking about?

130
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:32,519
Mom!

131
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,320
Mom!

132
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,039
Let me help you.

133
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:37,240
What's gotten into you today?

134
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,720
Before, when I asked you to help,

135
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,799
you couldn't be bothered.

136
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,159
Today you're so eager.

137
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,320
Tell me the truth.

138
00:08:43,399 --> 00:08:44,919
Did you do something you feel guilty about?

139
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,960
No, what is there to feel guilty about?

140
00:08:50,559 --> 00:08:51,440
I just feel like...

141
00:08:51,679 --> 00:08:53,159
you and Dad, for this family,

142
00:08:53,399 --> 00:08:54,279
have had it too hard.

143
00:08:55,559 --> 00:08:57,360
and I haven't been able to do much for you.

144
00:08:57,360 --> 00:09:00,120
As long as you're healthy and happy,

145
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,480
your dad and I will be satisfied.

146
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,960
You don't have to do anything.

147
00:09:14,039 --> 00:09:15,799
Xiaobei, is this your friend?

148
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:19,639
Mom, go upstairs first.

149
00:09:19,639 --> 00:09:20,799
I'll just talk to her for a minute.

150
00:09:20,799 --> 00:09:21,399
Okay.

151
00:09:24,639 --> 00:09:26,000
Mom, these clothes are all clean.

152
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,159
Just rinse them once more.

153
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:28,360
Okay.

154
00:09:29,679 --> 00:09:30,720
What are you doing here?

155
00:09:30,879 --> 00:09:31,799
I didn't expect

156
00:09:32,639 --> 00:09:33,840
you to actually switch back.

157
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:34,720
I told you.

158
00:09:35,639 --> 00:09:37,440
I'd only be Sheng Yuanzhou for 30 days.

159
00:09:39,679 --> 00:09:41,879
Today is your Zero Day.

160
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:42,879
Starting at midnight,

161
00:09:42,879 --> 00:09:44,679
you'll go back to your original identity.

162
00:09:44,679 --> 00:09:46,960
But if, within 24 hours,

163
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,879
you use the Key of Fate to dine with the Sheng family,

164
00:09:48,879 --> 00:09:50,679
you can switch back to being Sheng Yuanzhou.

165
00:09:50,679 --> 00:09:52,120
I've already spoken to my contact in the Sheng family,

166
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,080
and given her a heads-up.

167
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:55,399
She'll have food ready for you in the kitchen.

168
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:56,360
Go in through the back door.

169
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,600
Just finish eating in the kitchen.

170
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:58,679
No need.

171
00:09:58,919 --> 00:09:59,639
Why?

172
00:10:00,799 --> 00:10:03,440
Because I've already avenged my sister.

173
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:05,279
And I sent Zhu Zipeng to prison.

174
00:10:05,519 --> 00:10:07,399
And I let Sheng Yuanzhou and Lin Siqi

175
00:10:07,399 --> 00:10:08,720
smoothly end their engagement.

176
00:10:09,039 --> 00:10:11,039
And the relocation mess is over now.

177
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,799
So why would I go back to being Sheng Yuanzhou?

178
00:10:12,879 --> 00:10:13,759
I don't believe it.

179
00:10:13,759 --> 00:10:15,440
After living the Sheng family life,

180
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,960
you can still come back to a slum like this.

181
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:19,200
I want to stay with my family.

182
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,559
To share their hardships.

183
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:22,600
Your family doesn't need your company.

184
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,799
They need you to give them money,

185
00:10:23,799 --> 00:10:25,200
and give them a better life.

186
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:28,000
You should treasure the chance to be Sheng Yuanzhou.

187
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:30,320
That's the only way you can turn things around for them.

188
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:33,399
If you go back to being broke Zhang Xiaobei,

189
00:10:34,039 --> 00:10:35,960
back to this ant-like existence,

190
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,279
you won't be able to do anything.

191
00:10:37,399 --> 00:10:39,120
You can't help your family at all.

192
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:41,039
What's the benefit of being Sheng Yuanzhou again?

193
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,360
All the money

194
00:10:43,639 --> 00:10:45,559
is controlled by Sheng Shizhong.

195
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:47,360
Even when I tried to buy my parents a home,

196
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,559
he had it returned.

197
00:10:48,559 --> 00:10:50,120
So what do my parents actually get out of it?

198
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,159
True.

199
00:10:51,279 --> 00:10:53,559
Right now, Sheng Yuanzhou is still too weak.

200
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:54,759
There's no way for you to take control of

201
00:10:54,759 --> 00:10:56,120
the Shengshi Group's wealth.

202
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:58,200
But if you become Sheng Yuanzhou again, you still have a chance.

203
00:10:58,200 --> 00:11:00,159
As long as you stay in Sheng Yuanzhou's place,

204
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:02,000
I can help your parents unconditionally.

205
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,840
I can get them a new home,

206
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:05,039
find them a shop to do business,

207
00:11:05,039 --> 00:11:06,279
and give them a sum of money.

208
00:11:06,279 --> 00:11:08,200
I can buy you time

209
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:10,200
to become someone who can go up against Sheng Shizhong.

210
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:20,279
You're already Sheng Yuanzhou's fiancee now.

211
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:21,919
And Sheng Shizhong trusts you, too.

212
00:11:21,919 --> 00:11:23,759
Why are you so fixated on me?

213
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,840
Don't tell me you actually like me.

214
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:35,360
In my world, there's no romance.

215
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:38,399
I just think we're alike.

216
00:11:38,399 --> 00:11:39,879
We both know exactly what we want.

217
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:42,000
Jiang Lai, I'm not like you.

218
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:43,080
Not at all.

219
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,399
Family and kinship

220
00:11:45,039 --> 00:11:47,240
matter way more to me than money.

221
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:49,240
After my experiences this past month,

222
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:52,039
I understand even more how precious love and family are.

223
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:54,519
So I hope your high road is smooth.

224
00:11:54,519 --> 00:11:56,159
But I'm taking my narrow path.

225
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,879
I don't believe this is your final choice.

226
00:11:59,039 --> 00:11:59,679
I get it.

227
00:11:59,679 --> 00:12:01,200
You want a one-day trip back home.

228
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:02,399
But friendly reminder:

229
00:12:02,399 --> 00:12:03,919
you've only got 16 hours left.

230
00:12:16,279 --> 00:12:17,120
Who are you?

231
00:12:22,879 --> 00:12:25,080
You mortgaged the land your mother left you.

232
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:26,720
I...

233
00:12:33,799 --> 00:12:35,120
Zhang Xiaobei.

234
00:12:37,879 --> 00:12:39,399
Sheng Yuanzhou.

235
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:44,720
Come in.

236
00:12:49,879 --> 00:12:51,759
Father, you wanted to see me?

237
00:12:52,279 --> 00:12:53,000
Come on.

238
00:12:53,799 --> 00:12:54,919
You're coming with me to take care of something.

239
00:12:58,399 --> 00:12:59,799
What are you doing? What are you doing?

240
00:12:59,799 --> 00:13:00,440
Don't throw that away!

241
00:13:04,399 --> 00:13:05,080
What are you doing?

242
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,720
Xiaobei, your dad wasn't home,

243
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:09,720
so they rushed right in.

244
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:13,039
Sheng Yuanzhou.

245
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:17,320
Today's the final deadline to move.

246
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:19,399
But your relocation compensation hasn't arrived yet.

247
00:13:19,399 --> 00:13:20,440
Do you never go online?

248
00:13:20,799 --> 00:13:22,080
It's already been debunked online.

249
00:13:22,159 --> 00:13:23,559
That video is suspected to be fake.

250
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:25,200
So we've canceled the extra compensation.

251
00:13:26,039 --> 00:13:27,639
You have to move out today.

252
00:13:27,799 --> 00:13:29,440
Do you really have to take it this far?

253
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:30,600
Business is business.

254
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:47,679
Chairman Sheng Shizhong,

255
00:13:47,799 --> 00:13:49,200
you're already very rich.

256
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:51,120
Why can't you just spare people like us?

257
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:53,159
The things in our home, to you,

258
00:13:53,159 --> 00:13:54,840
are just pocket change.

259
00:13:55,559 --> 00:13:56,600
Money is money.

260
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:57,840
There's no big or small.

261
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:59,080
You're just greedy.

262
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:04,440
I respect money.

263
00:14:04,799 --> 00:14:06,360
But you don't deserve respect.

264
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:09,639
Then that "respect" you talk about

265
00:14:09,639 --> 00:14:11,200
can it get you out of this predicament?

266
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:12,480
This world itself is

267
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:14,679
a jungle where the strong prey on the weak.

268
00:14:14,679 --> 00:14:15,720
There's only so much money.

269
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:17,440
If you want more in your own pocket,

270
00:14:17,440 --> 00:14:20,080
you have to snatch it from someone else's.

271
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:23,440
The essence of survival

272
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:25,159
is slaughter.

273
00:14:30,120 --> 00:14:31,840
I'll leave you with one last piece of advice.

274
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:34,480
If you don't want to be stepped on,

275
00:14:34,480 --> 00:14:36,600
then step on others first.

276
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:10,120
If you go back to being broke Zhang Xiaobei,

277
00:15:10,120 --> 00:15:11,480
you won't be able to do anything.

278
00:15:11,559 --> 00:15:13,240
You can't help your family at all.

279
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:33,320
Siqi.

280
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:38,080
Xiaobei, what are you doing here?

281
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:40,200
You've worked hard taking care of Uncle these days.

282
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:42,240
I just heard the nurse say

283
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:43,600
Uncle's been pretty stable lately.

284
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:45,600
How about we go on a date today?

285
00:15:49,120 --> 00:15:50,639
But aren't we...

286
00:15:50,759 --> 00:15:51,559
Come on.

287
00:15:51,919 --> 00:15:53,679
You like it? I bought it just for you.

288
00:16:03,799 --> 00:16:04,679
Xiaobei.

289
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:07,600
Why did you suddenly come back again?

290
00:16:08,200 --> 00:16:10,720
Why is it that sometimes

291
00:16:11,559 --> 00:16:13,240
it feels like you've become someone else,

292
00:16:13,559 --> 00:16:15,600
like you're two different people?

293
00:16:16,320 --> 00:16:18,840
I don't understand what you're talking about.

294
00:16:20,039 --> 00:16:21,519
They've got the ice cream you like over there.

295
00:16:21,759 --> 00:16:22,519
Want some?

296
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:24,440
Let's go.

297
00:16:29,879 --> 00:16:30,440
Hello

298
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:32,320
One strawberry with chocolate syrup,

299
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:33,919
and some crushed Oreos.

300
00:16:34,559 --> 00:16:35,200
Thanks

301
00:16:35,639 --> 00:16:35,960
Okay

302
00:16:37,399 --> 00:16:39,799
Why does it feel like that familiar Zhang Xiaobei

303
00:16:39,799 --> 00:16:40,399
is back again

304
00:16:40,759 --> 00:16:41,399
Your ice cream

305
00:16:43,279 --> 00:16:43,840
Thank you

306
00:16:44,879 --> 00:16:45,440
Here

307
00:16:55,240 --> 00:16:56,840
If it could stay like this

308
00:16:57,159 --> 00:16:58,159
that'd be great
